description: Welcome to Holy Cacao, a sweet little dessert trailer in the heart of Austin, Texas. Stop on by today and treat yourself to a cake shake or frozen hot chocolate or cake ball on a stick. Can’t make it to Austin? Not to worry, in a few clicks our cake balls can be shipped to you.Holy Cacao cake balls start as cakes baked from scratch using the highest quality, freshest ingredients around. Once these delicious cakes are cooled, they are crumbled together with freshly made frosting and the mixture is then rolled into a ball and dipped in chocolate. To make the cake balls “trailer chic” we put them on Popsicle Sticks.Here at Holy Cacao we believe dessert should be fun. There may be nothing serious about our attitude, but we are serious about taste.
name: Holy Cacao
